<h2> Northstowe Karate Club</h2>
<p>
Northstowe Karate Club opened Wednesday 3rd July 2024. We are a member of the <a href="https://jka.or.jp/en">Japan Karate Association</a> and teach a traditional Japanese martial art - Shotokan Karate. Sessions will be held every Wednesday 1830-1930 at The Cabin. It's a family friendly club, where children (6+) and adults can both train together.
</p>

<p>Your first lesson is always free! To book your first class please <a href="/contact/">get in touch</a> or turn up to one of our sessions. Please arrive 5 minutes early for your first session so you can be registered.
